<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BtrBlocks - Better building blocks for the cloud</title>

    {#- Add an arbitrary string to the bundle #}
    {%- css %}{% include "public/css/base.css" %}{% endcss %}
    {%- css %}{% include "public/css/home.css" %}{% endcss %}
    <style>{% getBundle "css" %}</style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                {%- from 'img/logo.svg' import logo %}
                {{ logo({ class: 'logo-img' }) }}
                BtrBlocks
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1 class="slogan">Better building blocks for the cloud</h1>
            <p class="description">Cloud apps are currently built on legacy tech and locked in hyperscalers' silos. BtrBlocks solves this by building foundational cloud-independent infrastructure services.</p>
            <form class="subscribe-form">
                <input type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
                <button type="submit" class="subscribe-btn">Subscribe</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="container">
        <div class="principles">
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Cloud-Independent</h3>
                <p>Break free from vendor lock-in with infrastructure services that work seamlessly across all major cloud providers. No proprietary APIs. No migration headaches.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Cloud-Native</h3>
                <p>Built for distributed systems from the ground up. Embraces containerization, microservices architecture, and dynamic orchestration without the complexity.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Modern Technology</h3>
                <p>Engineered with cutting-edge tech stacks to deliver significantly better performance, reliability, and scalability metrics that legacy solutions can't match.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mission">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="code-comment">/* Our mission */</span>
            <h2>Breaking down cloud silos</h2>
            <p>Current cloud is built on legacy tech and captured in silos. We are building foundational cloud-independent infrastructure services for cloud-native applications.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 BtrBlocks. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
